Shutdown Behavior

Shutdown Behavior: How should the insstance react when showdown is done using the OS?
  - Stop (default)
  - Terminate

This is not applicable when shutting down fomr AWS console
CLI Attribute: InstanceInitiatedShutdownBehavior


Termination Behavior

Enable termination protection:
  To protect against accidental termination in AWS Console or CLI

Exam Tip:
  We have an instance where shutdown behavior = terminate and enable terminate protection is ticked
  We shutdown the instance from the OS, what will happen? The instance will be terminated!
